'''2021年格陵蘭大選'''於2021年4月6日（星期二）舉行，選舉新一屆[[格陵兰议会|格陵兰议会]]的全數31名議員。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2021/apr/06/greenland-goes-to-the-polls-in-rare-earth-mining-election |title=Greenland goes to the polls in rare earth mining election |publisher=The Guardian |date=2021-04-06 |accessdate=2021-04-07 |archive-date=2021-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210604215729/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2021/apr/06/greenland-goes-to-the-polls-in-rare-earth-mining-election |dead-url=no }}</ref>反對一項大型開採稀土和鈾礦項目的左翼政黨[[因纽特人共同体|因纽特人共同体]]獲得12席，成為新一屆議會最大黨。<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.france24.com/en/europe/20210407-left-wing-party-opposed-to-rare-earth-mining-project-wins-greenland-election |title=Left-wing party opposed to rare earth mining project wins Greenland election |website=France 24 |date=2021-04-07 |accessdate=2021-04-07 |archive-date=2021-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210606124708/https://www.france24.com/en/europe/20210407-left-wing-party-opposed-to-rare-earth-mining-project-wins-greenland-election |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==背景==
在2020年11月，[[格陵兰总理|格陵兰時任总理]][[金·基尔森|金·基尔森]]在[[前进_(政党)|前进党]]的領導層選舉中輸給了{{tsl|en|Erik Jensen (Greenlandic politician)|埃里克·詹森}}。但是，基爾森並未卸任總理。兩者之間日益激烈的競爭以及對{{tsl|en|Kvanefjeld|克瓦讷高地礦山}}的分歧導致{{link-en|民主黨 (格陵蘭)|Democrats (Greenland)|民主黨}}退出聯合政府，使[[前进_(政党)|前进党]]和{{link-en|我们土地的后代|Nunatta Qitornai}}在[[格陵兰议会|格陵兰议会]]的31個席位中僅佔12個席位<ref>[https://www.arctictoday.com/greenlands-premier-loses-majority-ahead-of-new-legislative-session/ Greenland’s premier loses majority ahead of new legislative session] {{Wayback|url=https://www.arctictoday.com/greenlands-premier-loses-majority-ahead-of-new-legislative-session/ |date=20210413060109 }} Arctic Today, 8 February 2021</ref>。基爾森未能組建新的聯合政府，格陵兰议会投票決定[[提前選舉|提前舉行大選]]<ref>[https://www.arctictoday.com/greenland-will-hold-an-early-election/ Greenland’s parliament calls an early election] {{Wayback|url=https://www.arctictoday.com/greenland-will-hold-an-early-election/ |date=20210217193418 }} Arctic Today, 17 February 2021</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://europeelects.eu/2021/04/05/greenland-parliamentary-elections-independence-on-the-horizon/|title=Greenland Parliamentary Elections: Independence on the Horizon|last=Lehtinen|first=Julius|publisher={{tsl|en|Europe Elects||Europe Elects}}|language=en|date=2021-04-05|access-date=2021-04-06|archive-date=2021-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210406005619/https://europeelects.eu/2021/04/05/greenland-parliamentary-elections-independence-on-the-horizon/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

稀土開採是此選舉的關鍵問題，該島南部的{{tsl|en|Kvanefjeld|克瓦讷高地礦山}}在多場公開聽證會和政黨競選活動都被提及<ref>{{Cite web|date=2021-04-06|title=Greenland goes to the polls in rare earth mining election|url=http://www.theguardian.com/world/2021/apr/06/greenland-goes-to-the-polls-in-rare-earth-mining-election|access-date=2021-04-06|website=|publisher=Agence France-Press|language=en|via=the Guardian|archive-date=2021-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210413182423/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2021/apr/06/greenland-goes-to-the-polls-in-rare-earth-mining-election|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Overgaard|first=Sidsel|date=2021-04-06|title=Global Mining Industry Closely Monitors Greenland's Election|url=https://www.npr.org/2021/04/06/984656689/global-mining-industry-closely-monitors-greenlands-election|access-date=2021-04-06|website=NPR|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210406093505/https://www.npr.org/2021/04/06/984656689/global-mining-industry-closely-monitors-greenlands-election|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|last=Gronholt-Pedersen|first=Jacob|last2=Onstad|first2=Eric|date=2021-03-02|title=Mining magnets: Arctic island finds green power can be a curse|language=en|work=Reuters|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-rareearths-greenland-usa-china-insigh-idUSKBN2AU0FM|access-date=2021-04-06|archive-date=2021-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210403105352/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-rareearths-greenland-usa-china-insigh-idUSKBN2AU0FM|dead-url=no}}</ref>。反對黨[[因纽特人共同体|因纽特人共同体]]要求暫停鈾礦開採，對更廣泛的稀土礦開採項目提出了質疑，而執政的[[前进_(政党)|前进党]]則表示支持該項目，指會帶來經濟增長<ref>{{Cite web|last=Breum|first=Martin|date=2021-02-25|title=Greenland's snap election exposes global mineral demand|url=https://euobserver.com/world/151013|access-date=2021-04-06|website=EUobserver|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210411113601/https://euobserver.com/world/151013|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|date=2021-04-06|title=Greenland election shows divide over rare-earth metals mine|url=https://apnews.com/article/greenland-kim-kielsen-elections-europe-parliamentary-elections-8bfffd8d467b6c0bc3773413155b6300|access-date=2021-04-06|website=Associated Press|archive-date=2021-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210406195330/https://apnews.com/article/greenland-kim-kielsen-elections-europe-parliamentary-elections-8bfffd8d467b6c0bc3773413155b6300|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|last=Quinn|first=Colm|date=2021-04-06|title=Greenland’s Rare-Earth Election|url=https://foreignpolicy.com/2021/04/06/greenland-rare-earths-election/|access-date=2021-04-06|website=Foreign Policy|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-04-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210406110417/https://foreignpolicy.com/2021/04/06/greenland-rare-earths-election/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==選舉制度==
格陵蘭議會的31席由一個多議席選區以採用[[漢狄法|漢狄法]]的[[比例代表制|比例代表制]]產生。<ref>[http://www.electionguide.org/elections/id/2825/ Election Profile] {{Wayback|url=http://www.electionguide.org/elections/id/2825/ |date=20141204194739 }} IFES</ref><ref>{{cite journal |title=Electoral politics, party performance, and governance in Greenland: Parties, personalities, and cleavages in an autonomous subnational island jurisdiction |url=https://www.islandstudies.ca/sites/default/files/ISJZhangGreenlandElectoralPolitics.pdf |journal=Island Studies Journal |access-date=2021-04-07 |archive-date=2021-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210203160718/https://islandstudies.ca/sites/default/files/ISJZhangGreenlandElectoralPolitics.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>

